last_episode_to_air.name: Empire of Death (2)
last_episode_to_air.overview: The Doctor has lost, his ageless enemy reigns supreme, and a shadow is falling over creation. Nothing can stop the devastation... except, perhaps, one woman.

name: Doctor Who
overview: The Doctor and his companion travel across time and space encountering incredible friends and foes.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: The Doctor and Ruby Sunday travel through time and space on adventures to unknown lands, to the Regency era in England, to outer space worlds and the sixties.

episodes.name: Space Babies
episodes.overview: Ruby learns the Doctor's amazing secrets when he takes her to the far future. There, they find a baby farm run by babies. But can they be saved from the terrifying bogeyman?

episodes.name: The Devil's Chord
episodes.overview: The Doctor and Ruby meet The Beatles but discover that the all-powerful Maestro is changing history. London becomes a battleground with the future of humanity at stake.

episodes.name: Boom
episodes.overview: Caught in the middle of a devastating war on Kastarion 3, the Doctor is trapped when he steps on a landmine. Can he save himself and Ruby, plus the entire planet... without moving?

episodes.name: 73 Yards
episodes.overview: Landing on the Welsh coast, the Doctor and Ruby embark on the strangest journey of their lives. In a rain-lashed pub, the locals sit in fear of ancient legends coming to life.

episodes.name: Dot and Bubble
episodes.overview: The world of Finetime seems happy and harmonious. But an awful terror is preying on the citizens. Can the Doctor and Ruby make them see the truth before it’s too late?

episodes.name: Rogue
episodes.overview: The Doctor and Ruby land in 1813, where guests at a duchess's party are being murdered and a mysterious bounty hunter called Rogue is about to change the Doctor's life forever.

episodes.name: The Legend of Ruby Sunday (1)
episodes.overview: The Doctor and UNIT investigate Ruby's past. But as the Time Window reveals horrifying secrets from Christmas Eve, the mysterious Triad Technology unleash the greatest evil of all.

episodes.name: Empire of Death (2)
episodes.overview: The Doctor has lost, his ageless enemy reigns supreme, and a shadow is falling over creation. Nothing can stop the devastation... except, perhaps, one woman.
